# isEmpty

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that denotes whether the option is empty.

## Declaration

```swift
var isEmpty: Bool { get }
```

## Discussion

Returns [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] if the option is equivalent to the empty set, or [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false] otherwise.

## Comparing compression options

- **contains(_:)**: Determines whether the supplied compression options are all present in the current instance.
- **intersects(_:)**: Determines whether the supplied compression options intersect with the current instance’s options.
